            "title": "帝柏海灣極低層3房1套連儲物室1,425萬元成交  原業主帳面虧損75萬元離場",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">香港置業奧運站一號銀海分行最新促成帝柏海灣一宗買賣成交，低層3房1套連儲物室的海景戶，放盤約半年，獲同區家庭客入市，新買家斥1,425萬元購入，實用呎價約 20,504元，屬市價成交。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">上述售出單位為帝柏海灣5座極低層，實用面積約695平方呎，屬3房1套連儲物室間隔，座向西南，享海景。雙方經議價後以1,425萬元承接，實用呎價約 20,504元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">資料顯示，業主於2019年5月以約1,500萬元購入上述單位，是次易手，帳面虧損約75萬元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/16286605-%e5%b8%9d%e6%9f%8f%e6%b5%b7%e7%81%a3%e6%a5%b5%e4%bd%8e%e5%b1%a43%e6%88%bf1%e5%a5%97%e9%80%a3%e5%84%b2%e7%89%a9%e5%ae%a41425%e8%90%ac%e5%85%83%e6%88%90%e4%ba%a4-%e5%8e%9f%e6%a5%ad%e4%b8%bb%e5%b8%b3",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20240726_PP_TRANSACTION_BP_FB.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-07-02 16:02:19",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "上海街165號全幢及163號1樓﹑3樓﹑5樓及天台標售",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">高力宣佈獲業主委託為首席代理公開出售位於香港佐敦上海街165號全幢及上海街163號1樓、3樓、5樓及天台。物業將以「現狀」及部份連租約形式出售。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/511x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/07/Shanghai-St-163-165_750.png.webp\">\n<img src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/511x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/07/Shanghai-St-163-165_750.png.webp\"/>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">是次出售的物業組合包含 8 個住宅單位及 1 個地舖。住宅總實用面積約 4,069 平方呎 (根據差餉物業估價署)，地舖建築面積則約 700 平方呎。目前除地舖外，住宅部分已全部租出，帶來即時且穩定的租金收入。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/16286322-%e4%b8%8a%e6%b5%b7%e8%a1%97165%e8%99%9f%e5%85%a8%e5%b9%a2%e5%8f%8a163%e8%99%9f1%e6%a8%93%ef%b9%913%e6%a8%93%ef%b9%915%e6%a8%93%e5%8f%8a%e5%a4%a9%e5%8f%b0%e6%a8%99%e5%94%ae",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/07/Shanghai-St-163-165_FB.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-07-02 15:41:31",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "日出康城MALIBU兩房中層戶成交945萬",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">利嘉閣地產調景嶺站分行新近促成將軍澳日出康城MALIBU 2A座中層E室的二手成交個案，單位實用面積約576方呎，採2房連儲物室間隔，外望草地景觀。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">新買家為區內客，業主原以950萬元放售，經誠意磋商後，終以合理價945萬元成交，折合實用面積呎價約16,406元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">據悉，原業主在2018年以約930.1萬元一手買入單位。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">該屋苑現時有約174個單位放盤，入場售價約由540萬元起。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/16286257-%e6%97%a5%e5%87%ba%e5%ba%b7%e5%9f%8emalibu%e5%85%a9%e6%88%bf%e4%b8%ad%e5%b1%a4%e6%88%b6%e6%88%90%e4%ba%a4945%e8%90%ac",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20240726_PP_TRANSACTION_BP_FB.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-07-02 15:32:15",
