            "title": "新地旗下海璇特色單位2億元成交",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">新地(00016) 旗下北角海璇今日(2日)錄得一宗特色戶大額招標成交，標售單位為海璇第1B期2座19樓A室，實用面積2,373平方呎連445平方呎平台，四房雙套間隔，連兩個車位，成交金額2億元，呎價84,282元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">單位造價及呎價創下發展項目新高，並同時打破港島東成交呎價最高紀錄。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/16286220-%e6%96%b0%e5%9c%b0%e6%97%97%e4%b8%8b%e6%b5%b7%e7%92%87%e7%89%b9%e8%89%b2%e5%96%ae%e4%bd%8d2%e5%84%84%e5%85%83%e6%88%90%e4%ba%a4",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/10/pp_new-flat-transaction_fb.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-07-02 15:27:13",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "午後再挫 滬指收跌83點 深指挫3.85% 兆易創新跌停板 金礦股逆市升",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">內地股市午後再度試底，滬深兩市股指均以跌幅擴大收場；兆易創新(03986)A股(603986.SH)終於跌停板，金礦股則尚能維持強勢。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"紫金礦業官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/10/02899-Web.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"紫金礦業官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/10/02899-Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">紫金礦業官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">上證綜指在今早初段一度跌69點或1.68%、見4,043點後，跌幅原本收窄，高位4,093點時跌幅縮至18點或0.46%，但午後重現拾級向下走勢，尾市終於跌穿早市低位，其後不斷尋底，最低見4,019點，跌93點才略為喘定；滬指最後收報4,028點，跌83點或2.03%，成交1.58萬億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">深證成指昨天已率先回吐，今日繼續跑輸，甫開市即失守萬六關，早市出現的全日高位15,886點時仍跌232點或1.44%，半日已跌逾2%，午後呈一浪低於一浪走勢，尾市跌幅擴大至600多點或超過4%，最低見15,453點，跌665點或4.13%，收市前略為回順；深指收報15,498點，挫620點或3.85%，成交1.87萬億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滬深300指數也跌146點或2.96%，以4,812點收市；創業板指數一度失守4,000點關口，收挫243點或5.71%，以4,017點收市。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"兆易創新官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/12/20261231_FI_03986_FB.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"兆易創新官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/12/20261231_FI_03986_FB.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">兆易創新官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">芯片及半導體相關板塊依然是重災區，兆易創新A股踏入午市不足20分鐘跌幅擴大至10%跌停板，報694.81元。瀾起科技(06809)A股(688008.SH)跌幅擴大至14.8%，收報269.15元；華虹宏力(01347)A股(688347.SH)同樣愈回愈深，收報284.5元，挫9.86%；中芯國際(00981)A股(688981.SH)跌6.72%，報144.1元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">金礦股尚能維持早市報升的狀況，紫金礦業(02899)A股(601899.SH)逆市升4.74%，報26.3元；赤峰黃金(06693)A股(600988.SH)早市已升10%漲停板，其後封板直到收市，報28.39元；山東黃金(01787)A股(600547.SH)升4.22%，報24.18元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/16285942-%e5%8d%88%e5%be%8c%e5%86%8d%e6%8c%ab-%e6%bb%ac%e6%8c%87%e6%94%b6%e8%b7%8c83%e9%bb%9e-%e6%b7%b1%e6%8c%87%e6%8c%ab3-85-%e5%85%86%e6%98%93%e5%89%b5%e6%96%b0%e8%b7%8c%e5%81%9c%e6%9d%bf-%e9%87%91%e7%a4%a6",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-13.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-07-02 15:11:31",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "港股午後險守二萬三關   比亞迪成大市主力",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">港股午後升幅續收窄，恒生指數現報23,001，升120或0.53%，險守二萬三關。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"資料圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/06/img_06aa3434_10.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"資料圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/06/img_06aa3434_10.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">資料圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒生科技指數倒跌，現跌0.49%或21點，報4450 ; 恒生國企指數升43點或0.58%，報7602點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">大市成交3,025.8億元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">比亞迪(01211)升7.94%，報78.2元，貢獻恒指31點，為表現最佳藍籌股及恒指最大貢獻者。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">石藥(01093)升7.46%，報7.49元 ; 信達生物(01801)升6.09%，報84.45元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">中芯(00981)跌插11.3%，報79.3元，為表現最差藍籌股 ; 聯想(00992)跌5.12%，報21.84元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/16285725-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e5%8d%88%e5%be%8c%e9%9a%aa%e5%ae%88%e4%ba%8c%e8%90%ac%e4%b8%89%e9%97%9c-%e6%af%94%e4%ba%9e%e8%bf%aa%e6%88%90%e5%a4%a7%e5%b8%82%e4%b8%bb%e5%8a%9b",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/HKSTOCK-6.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-07-02 15:06:36",
